author: Pixar
description:
Be the first to watch #Elio at home! 💫🛸 Buy it on Digital August 19 & Blu-ray™️ September 9.

Pre-Order now on Digital: https://movies.disney.com/elio

Take your family on an interstellar adventure with
Disney and Pixar’s Elio on August 19 via digital platforms including Amazon Prime 
Video, Apple TV, and Fandango at Home and September 9 on 4K UHD, Blu-ray and 
DVD.
The latest chapter in Disney and Pixar’s storytelling legacy will fulfill your sense of 
wonder about outer space when alien-obsessed Elio Solís suddenly has a close 
encounter of the intergalactic kind. After trying everything to contact extraterrestrials, 
Elio is thrilled when they not only respond, but beam him up to their cosmic 
“Communiverse”. Imagine his surprise when other planetary powers-that-be assume he 
is the leader of Earth! Elio’s experience in the Communiverse not only expands his 
horizons but teaches him how important it is to build connections with loved ones back 
on Earth.
